Please see http://www.tug.org/ for information about *Tex and
downloads for different platforms.

1. Install the following prerequisites:
    (a) texlive-xetex
    (b) texlive-latex
    () texlive-
    () texlive-
    () texlive-
    () texlive-
    () pgf
    () aspell
    () aspell-dict-<your_locale>
2. Modify the sections contained in the 'sections' subdirectory.
3. Run 'make' from the root directory of the project.
4. Use the generated PDF, XDV, or HTML files in 'build' subdirectory.
